WEBVTT

00:01:59.583 --> 00:02:01.059
as long as the work gets done.

00:02:01.083 --> 00:02:02.393
And by doing so,

00:02:02.417 --> 00:02:04.809
we make our employees ridiculously happy.

00:02:04.833 --> 00:02:07.292
And by doing that,
we get the best work from people.

00:02:07.958 --> 00:02:09.976
JB: We're seeing that people everywhere

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:13.976
are challenging these inherited,
default ways of working.

00:02:14.000 --> 00:02:16.684
They want access
to more choices, more agency,

00:02:16.708 --> 00:02:19.476
the freedom to decide
how they want to work.

00:02:19.500 --> 00:02:22.976
This supports them to better navigate
the tensions in their work and life

00:02:23.000 --> 00:02:25.851
for the sake of preserving
what's at stake for them.

